('144', 'Upon completion of the programme, students will have an insight into various aspects of European identity and integration, and will have the necessary skills for conducting independent research on a relevant topic.\n\n', 'NULL', 'NULL', 'website', 'objectives', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('144', 'The Identity and Integration track yields 60 ECTS credits: 42 credits for core courses and electives and 18 credits for a Master"s thesis.\n\nThe specific number of credits a student is required to obtain through coursework is determined by the admissi', 'ons committee and is based on the student"s previous qualifications. Fulfilment of all the requirements will take at least one year.', 'NULL', 'website', 'curriculum', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('144', 'European Studies: Identity and Integration provides a valuable foundation for students intending to teach or conduct independent research, or who are considering a career in advisory organisations, government and European Union institutions, internat', 'ional organisations or one of the writing professions.', 'NULL', 'website', 'job perspective', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('144', 'The Identity and Integration programme yields 60 ECTS credits: 18 credits for core courses, 24 credits for electives and 18 credits for a Master"s thesis.\n\n', 'NULL', 'NULL', 'website', 'curriculum', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
