('150', 'In forencic research, there is a growing need for scientists who can combine know-how in the fields of chemistry, biology, computer science or statistics with knowledge in the fields of criminology and law. The Forensic Science study programme trains', ' students to be innovative researchers or policy-makers who can make a contribution to the development of forensic science.', 'NULL', 'website', 'objectives', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('150', 'Criminal Law & Expert Evidence; the Chain of Evidence I and II; Policy, Ethics and Media; Forensic Statistics; Forensic Information Systems; Complex Crime Scenes and the Science of Collecting Trace Evidence.', 'NULL', 'NULL', 'website', 'curriculum', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('150', 'Lectures, research, branch-specific internship at an agency where forensic research plays a role.', 'NULL', 'NULL', 'website', 'instruction modes', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('150', 'All over the world forensic science is an important subject. Our programme distinguishes itself from others because it builds on general science instead of forensic science bachelors. As this is exactly the background of many employees of forensic la', 'boratories in (also) NFP countries, our programme obtains many requests from people in these countries. The high costs are often a barrier; becoming an NFP connected programme will much help', 'NULL', 'website', 'socio-economic contribution', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('150', 'Many of the forensic laboratory employees are lacking sufficient academic level. Our programme, being a Research Masters, prepares students towards forensic research. When graduated our students will give qualitative impulses to their home organizati', 'on. The quality, attitude and standards of the forensic laboratory personnel will thus improve', 'NULL', 'website', 'sustainable strengthening', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('150', 'Tuition fees are adjusted annually, for up to date information please see www.uva.nl/isp', 'NULL', 'NULL', 'website', 'tuition fee', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('150', 'The Master"s programme in Forensic Science is designed to train students to become researchers with a thorough knowledge of forensics. \n\nAlternatively, this Master qualifies graduates for careers in research at forensic institutes or forensic investi', 'gation agencies both within and outside the Netherlands, as well as at TNO, the RIVM or with the police force. Insurance companies, courts and ministries are also expected to have an increasing need for forensic science expertise.', 'NULL', 'website', 'job perspective', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('154', 'Depending on the area of specialization: basic knowledge and skills for jobs in the area of clinical linguistics, curriculum development, language engineering, speech technology, language planning, artificial intelligence.', 'NULL', 'NULL', 'website', 'objectives', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('154', 'Functional Grammar; Language Acquisition-, Technology, Speech Development and Pathology; Language Variation and Change; Sign Linguistics; Sociolinguistics and Creole Studies; Speech Communication-Technology; Theoretical Linguistics.', 'NULL', 'NULL', 'website', 'curriculum', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('154', 'Seminars and tutorials with supervision by specialists devoted to the in-depth study of a variety of topics. Supervised individual research resulting in a thesis. All classes are taught in small groups, with a maximum of 20 students.', 'NULL', 'NULL', 'website', 'instruction modes', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
