('160', 'Graduates are ready to start a career in any research environment where computation is the core business. Typically these are research groups within universities or research institutes, but can also be large supercomputing centres. The modelling and ', 'simulation skills of our graduates are highly appreciated and lead them to careers in many different types of organisations, including not only universities, but also financial institutes and other companies, hospitals and public organisations.', 'NULL', 'website', 'job perspective', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
