('166', 'International applicants that hold a bachelor"s degree in an area closely related to Information Studies can apply. The admissions board will assess the application to determine whether the applicant can be admitted to the study programme directly or', ' will have to follow a pre-Master"s programme first. \n\nFurthermore, international applicants must also fulfil general entry requirements set by the Faculty of Science regarding academic background, academic average and proficiency in English.', 'NULL', 'website', 'admission', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
