('167', 'Seminars and tutorials with supervision by specialists devoted to the in-depth study of a variety of topics. Supervised individual research resulting in a thesis. Most classes are taught in small groups, with a maximum of 20 students.', 'NULL', 'NULL', 'website', 'instruction modes', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
