('192', 'Among other things, the focus is on molecular cell biology; Molecular Phytopathology; Microbiology; Neurobiology; Biochemistry; Biophysics and Bioinformatics.', 'NULL', 'NULL', 'website', 'curriculum', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
