('192', 'By now, systems biology has been recognized both by academia and industry as an essential approach to many, if not all, biological questions and applications related to the living cell. Many of its constituents, from biochemistry to molecular and cel', 'l biology to computing and bioinformatics are expertises needed by universities and by companies, but the added value of a training that integrates them all results in excellent career perspectives.', 'NULL', 'website', 'job perspective', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('194', 'The programme focuses on the relationship between language structure and language use in various European languages and prepares students for advancement to a PhD programme.', 'NULL', 'NULL', 'website', 'objectives', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('194', 'Three core courses (research seminars), three elective tutorials, and three elective research seminars, plus an MA thesis. See website for further details.', 'NULL', 'NULL', 'website', 'curriculum', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
