('195', 'Literary Studies provides a valuable foundation for students who wish to go on to conduct independent research or who are considering a career in advisory organisations, scientific research organisations or the cultural sector.', 'NULL', 'NULL', 'website', 'job perspective', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('196', 'After completing this programme, students will have aquired a solid understanding of cultural and literary theory. Depending on the chosen specialisation, graduates often find employment as: editor for a publishing company, employee for a cultural or', ' scientific organisation, or teacher.', 'NULL', 'website', 'job perspective', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('196', 'The programme is divided into three main areas:\n Philosophy\n Cultural Studies\n Psychoanalysis\n\n', 'NULL', 'NULL', 'website', 'curriculum', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('196', 'This programme is intended for students with a Bachelors degree or\nan equivalent thereof in Literary Studies. The level of the Bachelors degree\nmust be comparable to that of a Dutch Bachelors degree.\n', 'NULL', 'NULL', 'website', 'admission', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('197', 'The origins of the ILLC trace far back into the twentieth century to the foundational work of Brouwer, Beth, Heyting and others. The goal of the ILLC (and as such the underlying spirit of the MSc in Logic) is to connect the traditional fundamental re', 'search in the formal sciences with a broad range of applications from information sciences to linguistics and philosophy.', 'NULL', 'website', 'objectives', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('197', 'Students can choose between 4 programmes: Logic & Mathematics: Focus on Mathematics of Modal Logic; Mathematical Analysis of Games and Set Theory; Logic & Computations: Focus on Games in Computer Science; Complexity Theory and Algorithms; Logic & Phi', 'losophy: Focus on Philosophy of Language and Cognitive Science; Logic & Language: Focus on Formal Models for Natural Language Semantics', 'NULL', 'website', 'curriculum', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('197', 'Lectures, research, thesis.', 'NULL', 'NULL', 'website', 'instruction modes', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('197', 'Tuition fees are adjusted annually, for up to date information please see www.uva.nl/isp', 'NULL', 'NULL', 'website', 'tuition fee', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('197', 'The MSc programme in Logic is a research-oriented programme. Most graduates of this programme continue their scientific education with PhD study. Many also carry out research in academic or industrial contexts, are teachers at schools or universities', ', work in the fields of publishing or journalism, or working in the software industry and management consulting.', 'NULL', 'website', 'job perspective', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('198', 'Following the interaction between general relativity and differential geometry, as well as between quantum mechanics and functional analysis in the first half of the 20th century, we are currently witnessing a new golden age in mathematical physics.', 'NULL', 'NULL', 'website', 'objectives', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('198', 'At the Universiteit van Amsterdam, the frontlines in mathematics and physics meet through noncommutative geometry; String Theory; Quantization Theory; Operator Algebras; Topological Defects; Quantum Groups; Critical Phenomena; Conformal Field Theory;', ' Integrable Systems; Lie Theory; Algebraic Geometry; Applied Analysis and Other Topics.', 'NULL', 'website', 'curriculum', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('198', 'Lectures, research, seminars.', 'NULL', 'NULL', 'website', 'instruction modes', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('198', 'Tuition fees are adjusted annually, for up to date information please see www.uva.nl/isp', 'NULL', 'NULL', 'website', 'tuition fee', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('198', 'Students in the Master"s programme in Mathematical Physics can complete the programme with an emphasis on either research, communication and education skills or on society-oriented skills. Graduates are consequently well-equipped to pursue successful', ' careers in academia, industry and public service.', 'NULL', 'website', 'job perspective', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('199', 'To provide students with such a knowledge, abilities and insight into mathematics and related fields, that they are able to work as a mathematical professional (including teacher at a Dutch High School), or are qualified for a training as scientific ', 'researcher or designer. The education also aims at enlarging the insight in the sciences as a whole and in their role in society.', 'NULL', 'website', 'objectives', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('199', 'At the Korteweg-de Vries Institute for Mathematics (KdvI) of the Universiteit van Amsterdam mathematics can be studied in its full richness. This is for a large part due to the character of the KdV Institute, and its faculty. At the KdV Institute res', 'earch and education are mixed in a natural fashion, and pure and applied mathematics have fruitful interactions at various levels.', 'NULL', 'website', 'curriculum', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
