('199', 'Students in the Master"s programme in Mathematical Physics can complete the programme with an emphasis on either research, communication and education skills or on society-oriented skills. Graduates are consequently well-equipped to pursue successful', ' careers in academia, industry and public service.', 'NULL', 'website', 'job perspective', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('202', 'The programme favours an interdisciplinary focus on media as representational objects, cultural practices and cultural forms, while acknowledging the effects of technology and social forces on media contents and functions.', 'NULL', 'NULL', 'website', 'objectives', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('202', 'Three core courses, three elective seminars, three elective tutorials, and an MA thesis.', 'NULL', 'NULL', 'website', 'curriculum', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('202', 'Seminars and tutorials with supervision by specialists devoted to the in-depth study of a variety of topics. Supervised individual research resulting in a thesis. All classes are taught in small groups of a maximum of 20 students.', 'NULL', 'NULL', 'website', 'instruction modes', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('202', 'Tuition fees are adjusted annually, for up to date information please see www.uva.nl/isp', 'NULL', 'NULL', 'website', 'tuition fee', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('202', 'Graduates may  find employment in public sectors related to their field, such as government agencies, advisory boards, education, media and cultural institutions, as well as in museums, broadcasting compagnies, and digital publishing and archival org', 'anisations. There is and will continue to be a great demand for expertise in the areas of theorising audiovisual presentation and representation, multimodal information storage and retrieval, and the digital convergence of image, text and sound.', 'NULL', 'website', 'job perspective', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('205', 'Medical Informatics (MI) is a discipline concerned with solving information-related problems in the medical and healthcare sectors. As a Medical Informatician, you are an expert in information analysis, representation, system design, implementation a', 'nd evaluation, instead of an expert in developing the advanced technologies which underlie information systems.', 'NULL', 'website', 'objectives', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('205', 'The curriculum encompasses four closely related fields: Medical Treatment and Patient Care; Healthcare Organisation; Processes and Logistics; Information and Communication Technology. By studying these subjects as a coherent package, you are able to ', 'gain an integrated view of issues in MI during the programme.', 'NULL', 'website', 'curriculum', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('205', 'Tuition covers lectures and case studies, organised into modules on a semester-based system. The programme also features short multidisciplinary work placements, during which you learn to apply the knowledge gained in the classroom to practical worki', 'ng situations at a department of the AMC involved directly or indirectly with patient care.', 'NULL', 'website', 'instruction modes', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('205', 'Tuition fees are adjusted annually. For up-to-date information, please see www.uva.nl/isp', 'NULL', 'NULL', 'website', 'tuition fee', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('205', 'This degree reflects the broad insight you have gained about problems in medical information science and proves that you possess unique expertise which is of great value on the labour market. \n\nAnother option is to continue your education and study f', 'or a PhD, either at the AMC or elsewhere.', 'NULL', 'website', 'job perspective', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('205', 'The curriculum takes an interdisciplinary approach to issues in Medical Informatics, framed within the overarching context of the healthcare organisation. It covers three related fields:\n- medical treatment and patient care\n- healthcare organisation,', ' processes and logistics\n- information and communication technology', 'NULL', 'website', '1st year', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('205', 'Semester 1 \n1: Current issues in medical informatics I 6 EC\n2: Knowledge representation & reasoning in medicine 6 EC\n3: Advanced data analysis in medicine 6 EC\n4: Biomedical information systems engineering 6 EC\n    Internship I 6 EC\nSemester 2 \n5: Bi', 'omedical research & evaluation methodology 6 EC\n6: Organisational settings of healthcare 6 EC\n7: Healthcare logistics & information systems 6 EC\n8: Information & process modelling in healthcare 6 EC\n    Internship II', 'NULL', 'website', 'after 1st year', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('205', 'The AMC-UvA promotes styding abroad. The international office of the AMC-UvA will support interested students where possible.', 'NULL', 'NULL', 'website', 'study abroad', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('205', 'The pre-Masters programme is financed through the use of contract education. The amount to be paid is associated with the number of ECTS credits that must be earned, with costs of approximately 40 per credit. \n\nThe tuition fee in 2011 was 1,', '713 for EU students and 12,000 for non-EU students.', 'NULL', 'website', 'tuition fee', 'http://www.studeren.uva.nl/ma-medical-informatics/object.cfm/A3138DAE-DD2A-4F4E-B6B1F86438C92AE5#p1'),
('206', 'Medical Anthropology and Sociology studies health, disease and health care from a social science perspective and how medical knowledge and practices are translated into health care structures. It investigates issues on health, society and culture and', ' familiarises students with the cultural worldviews and social economic forces that shape health and health care.', 'NULL', 'website', 'objectives', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('206', 'Contemporary Topics in Medical Anthropology and Sociology; Theorising Practice, Practising Theory; Childhood(s) in the Global South; Globalisation and new technologies of Health; Social and Cultural Studies of Sexuality; Theorising Gender; Research D', 'esign; Fieldwork and Thesis Project.', 'NULL', 'website', 'curriculum', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('206', 'Lectures, seminars, study visits, independent research, field work.', 'NULL', 'NULL', 'website', 'instruction modes', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('206', 'The programme consists of three core courses and one elective course. The core courses focus on the theoretical framework, research subjects for Medical and Social Anthropologists and the research design. Students also take one elective course on a t', 'heme or in an area that relates to their research interests. The programme is completed with a fieldwork of 8- 10 weeks and a thesis in the second semester.\n\nFor more information on the curriculum, please visit our website.\n\n', 'NULL', 'website', 'curriculum', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('206', 'After completion of the programme, students have:\n\n-acquainted themselves with social science theories and research practices that can be applied to the interface between health, society and culture\n-the ability to analyse practical health problems, ', 'formulate relevant objectives for Social Science research and compose research proposals\n-the skills they need to execute such research and report on it according to the applicable standards.', 'NULL', 'website', 'job perspective', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('207', 'The Research Master in Urban Studies combines the disciplines of urban geography, economic geography, urban and regional planning, and urban sociology, providing a multidisciplinary and comprehensive approach to urban change. An important theme throu', 'ghout the programme is the international comparison of urban phenomena. ', 'NULL', 'website', 'objectives', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('207', 'Urban Studies is two years long, and consists of a core introductory course, a number of research methodology and thesis preparation seminars, a research apprenticeship, one elective, a semester of fieldwork abroad, a written thesis and a research ar', 'ticle. Students are expected to obtain 60 ECTS credits in each year of the programme, totalling 120 ECTS. The first year will be spent in Amsterdam, the second year consists in a semester abroad followed by a period of thesis writing and research.', 'NULL', 'website', 'curriculum', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('207', 'Seminars and tutorials with supervision by specialists devoted to the in-depth study of a variety of topics. Supervised individual research resulting in a thesis. All classes are taught in small groups, with a maximum of 20 students. The curriculum i', 'ncludes a semester abroad.', 'NULL', 'website', 'instruction modes', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('207', 'Tuition fees are adjusted annually, for up to date information please see www.uva.nl/isp', 'NULL', 'NULL', 'website', 'tuition fee', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('207', 'Urban Studies is two years long, and consists of a core introductory course, a number of research methodology and thesis preparation seminars, a research apprenticeship, one elective, a semester of fieldwork abroad, a written thesis and a research ar', 'ticle. Students are expected to obtain 60 ECTS credits in each year of the programme, totalling 120 ECTS. The first year will be spent in Amsterdam, the second year consists in a semester abroad followed by a period of thesis writing and research.', 'NULL', 'website', 'curriculum', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('207', 'Graduates in Urban Studies are well prepared to continue their career in academia as PhD researchers. With their skills and knowledge, they will also have good chances to acquire strategic positions in public and semi-public organisations as policy-m', 'akers, consultants or in applied research projects. Students may also choose a commercial career working in sectors like real estate or property development.', 'NULL', 'website', 'job perspective', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('208', 'Migration and Ethnic Studies deals with the different forms, causes and consequences of international migration. It gives attention to the impact of globalisation, the regulation of international migration, the responses of international migrants to ', 'the changing opportunity structure. It addresses issues of immigrant incorporation, assimilation and diversity in various social fields.', 'NULL', 'website', 'objectives', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('208', 'Capita Selecta Social Theory; Dynamics in International Migration and Integration; Research Methodology; Urban Neighbourhoods and Communities; World Cities; Thesis.', 'NULL', 'NULL', 'website', 'curriculum', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('208', 'Lectures, seminars, study visits, independent research.', 'NULL', 'NULL', 'website', 'instruction modes', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('208', 'Tuition fees are adjusted annually, for up to date information please see www.uva.nl/isp', 'NULL', 'NULL', 'website', 'tuition fee', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('208', 'The Master"s programme in Migration and Ethnic Studies prepares students for doctoral study, further academic research and jobs in a variety of sectors, including advisory organisations, government institutions, non-governmental organisations and jou', 'rnalism.', 'NULL', 'website', 'job perspective', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('208', 'The programme consists of several core courses (30 ECTS credits total) and an elective of 10 ECTS, preferably relevant to the topic of the thesis. The programme is concluded with a Master"s thesis (20 ECTS). Fulfilling the requirements should take on', 'e year of full-time study.\n\nFor more information on the curriculum, please visit our website. ', 'NULL', 'website', 'curriculum', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('209', 'De master militair recht heeft 50 ec aan verplichte vakken en 10 ec aan keuzevakken', 'NULL', 'NULL', 'website', 'curriculum', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('209', 'De master is primair gericht op defensiepersoneel - militair en civiel - met een juridische aanstelling of degenen die een dergelijke aanstelling ambiren. Hij is ook bedoeld voor personen (civiel of militair) die een juridische advies of beleidsfun', 'ctie (wensen te) vervullen bij Defensie, Buitenlandse Zaken of Justitie; juristen aangesteld bij het Openbare Ministerie of in de militaire kamers van de Rechtbank of Gerechthof in Arnhem en officieren van de Koninklijke Marechaussee.', 'NULL', 'website', 'job perspective', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('210', 'Na afronding van het mastertraject Militaire geschiedenis beschik je over diepgaande kennis van het deelgebied Militaire geschiedenis. Dankzij deze specialisatie heb je betere perspectieven op de arbeidsmarkt dan met alleen een bachelordiploma. \n\nOp ', 'dit moment is de arbeidsmarkt krapper dan voorheen. Je zult na je master rekening moeten houden met een langere baanzoekduur, meer tijdelijke contracten en een lager startsalaris dat minder snel stijgt.', 'NULL', 'website', 'job perspective', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('210', 'De master is ook toegankelijk met een:\n- diploma Internationale Veiligheidsstudies van het Koninklijk Instituut voor de Marine*  \n- diploma Operatin van de Koninklijke Militaire Academie* \n- bachelordiploma Krijgswetenschap van de Nederlandse Defen', 'sie Academie* \nBen je in het bezit van een van bovenstaande diploma"s dan zal je via een aansluitprogramma eerst het vak wetenschapsfilosofie moeten afronden voordat je kan starten met het masterprogramma.', 'NULL', 'website', 'admission', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('214', 'Na afronding van de master kunnen alumni solliciteren naar een baan als beginnend conservator. Als alumnus beschik je niet alleen over gedegen theoretische kennis, maar heb je ook nog eens de nodige werkervaring opgedaan. Het merendeel van de afgestu', 'deerden heeft in korte tijd een baan gevonden, onder andere bij:\n\n-Van Gogh Museum \n-Rijksmuseum \n-Teylers Museum\n-Rijksdienst voor Kunsthistorische Documentatie \n\nOok is het mogelijk na afsluiting van de opleiding te promoveren.', 'NULL', 'website', 'job perspective', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('216', 'Are you interested in the music of India? Or would you like to study the development of modern twentieth-century compositions? The MA programme in Musicology will enable you to focus extensively on a subject within your own field of interest.', 'NULL', 'NULL', 'website', 'objectives', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('216', 'The programme yields 60 ECTS credits, with a courseload of 42 ECTS and a Thesis worth 18 ECTS.', 'NULL', 'NULL', 'website', 'curriculum', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('216', 'Courses are taught in the form of seminars, in groups of 10 to 15 students.', 'NULL', 'NULL', 'website', 'instruction modes', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('216', 'Tuition fees are adjusted annually. For up-to-date information, please see www.uva.nl/isp', 'NULL', 'NULL', 'website', 'tuition fee', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('216', 'The MA programme in Musicology aims to provide students\nwith a comprehensive understanding of one particular area of musicology. Graduates can pursue a career in the diverse artistic and cultural sectors, such as radio, television and other media, wo', 'rk as an adviser or manager of an orchestra, opera company, agency, concert hall or other cultural organisation. \nResearch careers at universities, academic libraries, music schools, conservatories and museums are also possible.\n', 'NULL', 'website', 'job perspective', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('216', 'The programme comprises 60 ECTS credits:\n\n* 30 credits for courses in Musicology\n* 12 credits for an elective in Musicology or another discipline\n* 18 credits for a Masters thesis', 'NULL', 'NULL', 'website', 'curriculum', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('217', 'The programme prepares students for a career in teaching, journalism or any of the other writing professions, as well as for an advisory or managerial position in a public organisation or government institution. It also provides students with the bas', 'ic knowledge and skills that will enable them to pursue a professional career at the academic level in any of the diverse fields of research or general education, particularly where the study of religion is involved.', 'NULL', 'website', 'job perspective', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('217', 'The programme aims to provide the student with the basic knowledge and skills that will enable him to pursue a professional career in various fields of Mysticism and Western esotericism, research or general education on an academic level.', 'NULL', 'NULL', 'website', 'objectives', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('217', 'Seminars and tutorials with supervision by specialists devoted to the in-depth study of a variety of topics. Supervised individual research resulting in a thesis. All classes are taught in small groups, with a maximum of 20 students.', 'NULL', 'NULL', 'website', 'instruction modes', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('217', 'Tuition fees are adjusted annually, for up to date information please see www.uva.nl/isp', 'NULL', 'NULL', 'website', 'tuition fee', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('218', 'Door de toenemende internationalisering komen er steeds meer mensen binnen onze landsgrenzen die het Nederlands als tweede taal moeten leren. Het onderwijs wordt steeds meer geprofessionaliseerd. Dat betekent dat er mensen nodig zijn die vanuit een a', 'cademisch denkkader bij kunnen dragen aan verbetering van dit onderwijs.\n', 'NULL', 'website', 'job perspective', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('218', 'NULL', 'NULL', 'NULL', 'website', 'tuition fee', 'http://www.studeren.uva.nl/ma-nederlands-als-tweede-taal'),
('219', 'In de bachelor en de aansluitende master wordt opgeleid tot fiscaal jurist en kun je gaan werken bij de belastingdienst, bij een belastingadvieskantoor of als zelfstandig belastingadviseur.', 'NULL', 'NULL', 'website', 'job perspective', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('220', 'Als je de onderzoeksmaster Nederlandse letterkunde hebt afgerond, beschik je over een grote kennis van literatuur, je hebt een goed analytisch vermogen, je kunt voortreffelijk formuleren, en weet wat er in de wereld van literatuur en letterkunde te k', 'oop is. Je weet niet alleen waar het in de actuele debatten over literatuur, cultuur, identiteit en onderwijs om gaat, je bent nu ook in staat je in die debatten te mengen.', 'NULL', 'website', 'job perspective', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('221', 'Na afronding van de master Nederlandse taal en cultuur beschik je over diepgaande kennis van een of meer deelgebieden van de neerlandistiek. Dankzij deze specialisatie - of juist verbreding - heb je betere perspectieven op de arbeidsmarkt dan met all', 'een een bachelordiploma. \n\nWil je les geven, dan volg je na de master de eenjarige lerarenopleiding (1,5 jaar in deeltijd) bij de Interfacultaire Lerarenopleidingen (ILO).', 'NULL', 'website', 'job perspective', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('223', 'The Master in New Media & Digital Culture is for students interested in contributing to timely discourse surrounding critical media theory. It builds upon the pioneering new media scene that Amsterdam is known for, with an emphasis on the study of In', 'ternet culture.', 'NULL', 'website', 'objectives', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('223', 'Courses are taught in the form of seminars, in groups of 10-15 students.', 'NULL', 'NULL', 'website', 'instruction modes', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('223', 'Tuition fees are adjusted annually, for up to date information please see www.uva.nl/isp', 'NULL', 'NULL', 'website', 'tuition fee', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('223', 'Graduates in New Media have the critical faculties, skills and outlook that will enable them to pursue a career in media or the creative and cultural industries, and to offer input at the conceptual level. New media researchers are in demand in a var', 'iety of industries and sectors, as each comes to terms with the importance of an advanced Web presence or the special skills necessary to work with the Internet. ', 'NULL', 'website', 'job perspective', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('225', 'Bij voltooiing van zowel de notarile bachelor als de notarile master aan de UvA voldoet de student aan de benoemingsvereisten van het Besluit Beroepsvereisten Kandidaat-notaris, en kan hij dus kandidaat-notaris worden. \n\n', 'NULL', 'NULL', 'website', 'job perspective', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('228', 'Het scala aan functies voor afgestudeerde onderwijskundigen is zeer breed. Je wordt niet alleen opgeleid tot wetenschapsbeoefenaar, maar ook tot een wetenschappelijk geschoolde onderwijskundige professional.\n', 'NULL', 'NULL', 'website', 'job perspective', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('228', 'Het is mogelijk om de stage of scriptie in het buitenland uit te voeren of (extra) mastermdoulen te volgen aan een buitenlandse universiteit.', 'NULL', 'NULL', 'website', 'study abroad', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('228', 'Voor studenten die de Master Onderwijskunde in deeltijdtempo volgen, geldt een aanbevolen volgorde. De mastermodulen en de stage en scriptie worden dan verdeeld over twee studiejaren.', 'NULL', 'NULL', 'website', 'curriculum', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('228', 'In de master Onderwijskunde aan de UvA worden als enige alle niveaus binnen de onderwijskunde bestudeert: micro (leerproces), meso (schoolorganisatie) en macro (beleid).', 'NULL', 'NULL', 'website', 'characteristics', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('230', 'Na afronding van het mastertraject Opvoedingsondersteuning beschik je over een gedegen overzicht van een specifiek vakgebied binnen de Pedagogische wetenschappen. Dankzij deze specialisatie heb je betere perspectieven op de arbeidsmarkt dan met allee', 'n een bachelordiploma.\n\nAfgestudeerden houden zich in de verschillende functies bezig met: \n-het geven van voorlichting en adviezen \n-het opzetten van preventieprojecten \n-beleidsanalyse\n-onderzoek doen\n-coordinatie/leidinggeven', 'NULL', 'website', 'job perspective', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('230', 'Het afstudeerproject wordt elk jaar door een aantal studenten in het buitenland uitgevoerd.', 'NULL', 'NULL', 'website', 'study abroad', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('230', 'Alle modulen worden gegeven in semester 1. Tegelijkertijd wordt al begonnen aan het afstudeerproject, dat in semester 2 verder uitgevoerd wordt. Voor het afstudeerproject worden studenten gekoppeld aan een van de instellingen die zich in september pr', 'esenteren en die een onderzoeksvraag (uit de praktijk) hebben.', 'NULL', 'website', 'curriculum', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('230', '- het is de enige masteropleiding waarbinnen studenten zich specialiseren op het gebied van opvoedingsondersteuning.\n- er is een directe koppeling tussen wetenschappelijke studie en onderzoek en de pedagogische praktijk.', 'NULL', 'NULL', 'website', 'characteristics', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('231', 'Het beroepsveld van orthopedagogen heeft betrekking op de institutionele en relationele pedagogische benadering van kinderen en jongeren die door leer- of gedragsproblemen, ziekte of handicap in hun ontwikkeling worden bedreigd, bijv. het speciaal on', 'derwijs, de jeugdhulpverlening, of de kinderbescherming. Daarnaast zijn er beleidsfuncties met betrekking tot het vormgeven van het onderwijs in het kader van landelijke operaties zoals leerlinggebonden financiering of weer-samen-naar-school.', 'NULL', 'website', 'job perspective', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('231', 'Het mastertraject Orthopedagogiek is een voltijdsprogramma van 1 jaar, maar kan gevolgd worden in deeltijdtempo. In deeltijdtempo is de duur (minimaal) 2 jaar.', 'NULL', 'NULL', 'website', 'curriculum', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('231', 'Het is mogelijk om de stage of scriptie in het buitenland uit te voeren of (extra) mastermodulen te volgen aan een buitenlandse universiteit.', 'NULL', 'NULL', 'website', 'study abroad', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('233', 'The Research Master"s programme in Educational Sciences integrates pedagogical research and educational research. Both disciplines are characterised by empirical research into learning and development processes in various settings, that is carried ou', 't with advanced quantitative and qualitative techniques.', 'NULL', 'website', 'objectives', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('233', 'Students choose from disciplinary courses that give systematic overview of fundamental, theory-driven research into the nature, development, and explanation of child attributes. Research topics share the bioecological model as common theoretical fram', 'ework. In addition to a selection of disciplinary courses, students take an introductory course on bioecological models, courses in methods and statistics, a course in writing and presentation skills, and carry out two research projects.', 'NULL', 'website', 'curriculum', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('233', 'Tuition fees are adjusted annually. For up-to-date information, please see www.uva.nl/isp.', 'NULL', 'NULL', 'website', 'tuition fee', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('233', 'It is possible to do a clinical internship ("stage") as part of the "clinical route" in the Research Master"s programme. ', 'NULL', 'NULL', 'website', 'instruction modes', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('233', 'Students choose from disciplinary courses that give a systematic overview of fundamental, theory-driven research into the nature, development, and explanation of child attributes. In addition to a selection of disciplinary courses, students take an i', 'ntroductory course on bioecological models, courses in methods and statistics, and a supporting course in writing and presentation skills. Each student carries out two research projects.', 'NULL', 'website', 'curriculum', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('233', 'Following successful completion of the programme, students are qualified to apply for an existing PhD project or to create their own PhD project by submitting a PhD project proposal and applying for a research grant. Students can also apply for a pos', 'ition in applied research, such as in the Division of Applied Research of the SCO-Kohnstamm Institute or UvA/Virenze. Such positions often lead to a PhD degree. Students may also find research jobs elsewhere, such as in the public or private sector.', 'NULL', 'website', 'job perspective', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('233', '- Students get intensive guidance during the two year programme.\n- The instituition offers housing for international students. Jelka Driehuis is the international coordinator in the department of Child Development and Education, international.office@', 'fmg.uva.nl. \n', 'NULL', 'website', 'international', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('233', '- Students get intensive guidance during the two year programme.\n- The instituition offers housing for international students. Jelka Driehuis is the international coordinator in the department of Child Development and Education, international.office@', 'fmg.uva.nl. \n', 'NULL', 'website', 'international', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('233', 'The following additional criteria apply:\n- Good writing skills, as indicated by written academic work.\n- Sufficient active and passive proficiency in English. \n- An active interest in research.\n- The ambition to become a researcher.', 'NULL', 'NULL', 'website', 'admission', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('233', 'Students may choose to do their research abroad, taking advantage of the national and international contacts of the Research Master"s staff members.', 'NULL', 'NULL', 'website', 'study abroad', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('233', 'The courses are organised in small groups, allowing for intensive interaction between staff members and students. Presentation is not only done by the staff members, but also by students who are invited to present and comment upon topics of interest.', ' In the methodological/statistical courses, advanced designs and techniques are presented and illustrated with applications in the Educational Sciences. Furthermore, the students practice relevant skills.', 'NULL', 'website', 'instruction modes', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('233', 'The following additional criteria apply:\n- Good writing skills, as indicated by written academic work.\n- Sufficient active and passive proficiency in English. \n- An active interest in research.\n- The ambition to become a researcher.\n', 'NULL', 'NULL', 'website', 'admission', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('238', 'The Master"s programme in Urban and Regional Planning consists consists the following elements:\n\nPlanning Methodologies (6 ECTS)\nInnovative Planning Practices (6 ECTS)\nStrategic Planning (6 ECTS)\nTransport Planning (6 ECTS)\nArea Develo', 'pment and Real Estate (6 ECTS)\nMethods & Techniques (thesis preparation) (6 ECTS)\nThesis (24 ECTS)\n\nPlease note that the curriculum is still under construction. For up-to-date information on the curriculum, please visit our website.\n', 'NULL', 'website', 'curriculum', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('238', 'Students with a Master"s degree in Urban and Regional Planning can expect enhanced career opportunities in the public domain as well as in the private sectors.\n\nThere are a number of possible employers in the public domain e.g. ministries, provinces ', 'or municipalities while in the private sector there are opportunities in housing corporations, within real estate or research/consultancy firms for spatial issues.', 'NULL', 'website', 'job perspective', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('240', 'Participants will gain in-depth theoretical knowledge, acquire the necessary work experience and can therefore work at various institutions, such as archives, museums, film houses and festivals.', 'NULL', 'NULL', 'website', 'objectives', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('240', 'Seminars and tutorials with supervision by specialists devoted to the in-depth study of a variety of topics. Supervised individual research resulting in a thesis. All classes are taught in small groups, with a maximum of 20 students. Full-time intern', 'ship of several months, and excursions.', 'NULL', 'website', 'instruction modes', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('240', 'Tuition fees are adjusted annually, for up to date information please see www.uva.nl/isp', 'NULL', 'NULL', 'website', 'tuition fee', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('240', 'This Master"s programme is unique in Europe for combining archiving and programming skills from an in-depth theoretical and practical perspective. Given the ever-expanding market in image-based culture, education and entertainment, courses such as th', 'is create excellent career opportunities for graduates in such areas as archives, museums, film houses and festivals.', 'NULL', 'website', 'job perspective', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('241', 'In de master privaatrechtelijke rechtspraktijk moet je voor 15 ec verplichte vakken volgen en voor 35 ec keuzevakken. Voor de keuzevakken kun je kiezen uit verschillende profielen: onderneming en privaatrecht; sociaal privaatrecht; privaatrecht algem', 'een  ', 'NULL', 'website', 'curriculum', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('241', 'De master Privaatrechtelijke rechtspraktijk leidt op voor de traditionele togaberoepen\n(advocatuur, rechterlijke macht) en het bedrijfsleven. Door het ruime aanbod van keuzevakken is de master ook bij uitstek geschikt voor beroepen in de internationa', 'le handel of de sociaal-juridische hulpverlening.', 'NULL', 'website', 'job perspective', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('243', 'Meer informatie is te vinden in de brochure "studeren in het buitenland": http://psychologyincludes.edu.fmg.uva.nl/owi/internat_office/Brochure%20Uitgaand%201011.pdf\n', 'NULL', 'NULL', 'website', 'study abroad', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('243', 'De mogelijkheden op de arbeidsmarkt zijn groot. Waar je terechtkomt, is mede afhankelijk van je afstudeerrichting:\nDit zijn slechts enkele grepen uit de vele mogelijkheden.\nVeel afgestudeerde psychologen komen in meer algemene beroepen terecht.', 'NULL', 'NULL', 'website', 'job perspective', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('243', 'Na je bachelor Psychologie kun je bij de UvA kiezen uit diverse masterprogramma"s. Je kunt je specialiseren op uiteenlopende gebieden. Bijvoorbeeld in de arbeids-en organisatiepsychologie, klinische psychologie, en brein & cognitie. Daarnaast is de U', 'vA de enige Nederlandse universiteit die de master Psychologische Methodenleer aanbiedt. ', 'NULL', 'website', 'characteristics', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('243', 'Het curriculum van de master psychologie hangt af van de specialisatie die wordt gevolgd. Bij de specialisatie Brein & Cognitie komen bijvoorbeeld onderwerpen als geheugen, perceptie en bewustzijn aan bod, terwijl bij de specialisatie Arbeids- en Org', 'anisatiepsychologie dieper in wordt gegaan op onderwerpen als besluitvorming, personeelsselectie, leiderschap, of creativiteit. ', 'NULL', 'website', 'curriculum', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('243', 'Op de UvA specialiseren psychologiestudenten zich al in het derde bachelorjaar. Als eis voor het volgen van een bepaalde masterspecialisatie geldt daarom ook dat de bijbehorende bachelorspecialisatie is afgerond. Om toegelaten te worden tot bijvoorbe', 'eld de masterspecialisatie Brein & Cognitie is het verplicht om de bachelorspecialisatie Brein & Cognitie te hebben afgerond.', 'NULL', 'website', 'admission', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('243', 'In de masterprogrammas ligt de nadruk op zelfstandig werken en wordt de meeste tijd\nbesteed aan een stage en het zelfstandig uitvoeren van een onderzoek, uitmondend in het\nmasterthese. De stage en de masterthese vormen samen een meesterproef', ' waarin men\naantoont alle opgedane kennis en vaardigheden te kunnen toepassen. Verder volgt men in\nde masterprogrammas specialistisch onderwijs dat voorbereidt op de afstudeeropdracht.', 'NULL', 'website', 'instruction modes', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('244', 'Having successfully completed the Research Master"s programme, the students will have acquired sufficient knowledge and specific skills to independently carry out high quality research. As such, this programme forms an excellent basis for a PhD posit', 'ion, although it was not set up exclusively to this end.', 'NULL', 'website', 'objectives', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('244', 'The Research Master Psychology provides the opportunity to specialise in any of the major fields of Psychology: Clinical Psychology, Developmental Psychology, Psychonomics, Psychological Methods, Social Psychology, and Work and Organisational Psychol', 'ogy. Students choose one field for their major, and one for their minor.', 'NULL', 'website', 'curriculum', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('244', 'Courses are taught in informal, highly interactive, small groups settings. Teaching is broadly tailored to this setting and includes student participation in discussions, presentations, reviews, and direct feedback. The programme is aimed at acquirin', 'g active knowledge (as manifest in papers, presentations, research proposals), rather than reproducing knowledge (e.g. written examinations).', 'NULL', 'website', 'instruction modes', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('244', 'Tuition fees are adjusted annually, for up to date information please see http://www.studeren.uva.nl/finance', 'NULL', 'NULL', 'website', 'tuition fee', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('244', 'After graduation students are eligible to pursue a career as researcher at the university. Graduates may decide to pursue a PhD programme and work towards a doctorate in disciplines directly related to this research programme. Graduates are also well', ' qualified for a career in scientific research in companies and governmental organizations. Also, graduates may find employment as policy maker in the public sector relevant to their field, such as government agencies, advisory boards and education.', 'NULL', 'website', 'job perspective', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('244', 'In order to further enhance the scope and breadth of the programme, students are encouraged to carry out one of the two research projects abroad.  ', 'NULL', 'NULL', 'website', 'study abroad', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('244', 'Please refer to http://www.studeren.uva.nl/finance', 'NULL', 'NULL', 'website', 'tuition fee', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('244', 'Over a two-year period, students complete advanced courses on research methods and statistics. Furthermore, students will be trained in computer skills (programming) and writing and presentation skills. During the remaining time, students will take c', 'ourses in two fields of their choice and receive excellent research experience.', 'NULL', 'website', 'curriculum', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('246', 'De master Redacteur/editor is helemaal gericht op een baan in de boekenwereld. Academici met een achtergrond in de geesteswetenschappen blijken in de uitgeverswereld als redacteur erg in trek te zijn.', 'NULL', 'NULL', 'website', 'job perspective', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('246', 'NULL', 'NULL', 'NULL', 'website', 'tuition fee', 'http://www.studeren.uva.nl/ma-redacteur-editor'),
('249', 'To provide a valuable foundation for students who will be conducting independent PhD research, and for those who are considering a career in advisory organisations, scientific research organisations, cultural activities and writing professions.', 'NULL', 'NULL', 'website', 'objectives', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('249', 'The Research Master"s programme in Religious Studies yields 120 ECTS credits: 90 credits for core courses, electives and tutorials and 30 credits for a Master"s thesis.', 'NULL', 'NULL', 'website', 'curriculum', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('249', 'Seminars and tutorials with supervision by specialists devoted to the in-depth study of a variety of topics. Supervised individual research resulting in a thesis. All classes are taught in small groups, with a maximum of 20 students.', 'NULL', 'NULL', 'website', 'instruction modes', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('249', 'Tuition fees are adjusted annually, for up to date information please see www.uva.nl/isp', 'NULL', 'NULL', 'website', 'tuition fee', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('249', 'The Research Master"s programme in Religious Studies provides a valuable foundation for those students who wish to pursue independent PhD research, and for those considering a career in advisory organisations, scientific research organisations, the c', 'ultural sector or any of the writing professions.', 'NULL', 'website', 'job perspective', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('250', 'Tuition fees are adjusted annualy. See for the latest news www.uva.nl/isp', 'NULL', 'NULL', 'website', 'tuition fee', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('250', 'First and foremost, the programme provides a solid foundation for PhD research in argumentation, rhetoric, discourse analysis, philosophy of language and cultural analysis. It also provides a solid basis for a career in professions in which the criti', 'cal analysis, sound evaluation and sophisticated production of argumentative discourse play an important part.', 'NULL', 'website', 'job perspective', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('255', 'Gender, Sexuality and Society is devoted to enhancing the understanding of differences between groups of women and groups of men as well as between women and men in an era of globalisation and transnational migration. Structurally embedded norms conc', 'erning gender relations and sexual behaviour are addressed together with variables such as class, ethnicity, religion, age and political ideology.', 'NULL', 'website', 'objectives', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('255', 'Capita Selecta Social Theory; Social and Cultural Studies of Sexuality; Sexuality, Ethnicity and Class; Theorising Gender; Research Methods; Thesis.', 'NULL', 'NULL', 'website', 'curriculum', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('255', 'Seminars, lectures, audiovisual presentations, essays.', 'NULL', 'NULL', 'website', 'instruction modes', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('255', 'Tuition fees are adjusted annually, for up to date information please see www.uva.nl/isp', 'NULL', 'NULL', 'website', 'tuition fee', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('255', 'The Master"s programme in Gender, Sexuality and Society prepares students both for further research and for jobs in a variety of sectors, including:\n\n-advisory organisations, \n-government institutions, \n-non-governmental organisations, \n-journalism.\n', 'NULL', 'NULL', 'website', 'job perspective', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('255', 'This programme starts in September. The programme consists of several core courses (30 ECTS credits total):\n\none on gender and sexuality\none on the main debates in the social sciences\nand one on methodology\nand an elective of 10 ECTS, prefer', 'ably relevant to the topic of the thesis.\n\nThe programme is concluded with a Master"s thesis (20 ECTS) based on a topic of the students choice. \n\nFor more information on the curriculum, please visit our website.', 'NULL', 'website', 'curriculum', 'http://studieadres.nl');
INSERT INTO `program_links` (`program_id`, `summary1`, `summary2`, `summary3`, `type`, `subject`, `weblink`) VALUES
('257', 'Social Policy and Social Work in Urban Areas studies the ways in which social problems in urban areas are defined and solved and analyses the roles ascribed to professionals in these processes. It is designed to equip tomorrow"s leading social profes', 'sionals, policy makers, researchers, public sector managers and advisers with the combination of insights and skills they will need.', 'NULL', 'website', 'objectives', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('257', 'Capita Selecta Social theory; Research Methods; Social problems in Urban Areas; Active Citizenship; European Social Policy; Social Interventions; Thesis.', 'NULL', 'NULL', 'website', 'curriculum', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('257', 'Lectures, seminars and research projects.', 'NULL', 'NULL', 'website', 'instruction modes', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('257', 'Tuition fees are adjusted annually, for up to date information please see www.uva.nl/isp', 'NULL', 'NULL', 'website', 'tuition fee', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('257', 'This track in the Masters programme in Sociology is designed for those who are involved or interested in comparative social policy and social problems in urban areas. \n\nThis programme is unique in focusing on social policy at both the local execut', 'ive level and the level of evidence-based policy making and policy design. It is expected that there will be an increasing demand for professionals who are able to combine these complementary perspectives.', 'NULL', 'website', 'job perspective', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('257', 'The programme consists of several core courses (30 ECTS credits) and an elective of 10 ECTS (or two electives of 5 ECTS each), preferably relevant to the topic of the thesis. The programme is concluded with a Master"s thesis (20 ECTS). \n\nFor more inf', 'ormation on the curriculum, please visit our website.', 'NULL', 'website', 'curriculum', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('258', 'The Research Master"s programme Social Sciences offers advanced training in social science theory and innovative methodologies in a rigorous and multidisciplinary social science research environment. It trains students to conduct research along both ', 'empirical-analytical and interpretive lines, approach their research from a historical perspective, appreciate both local detail and global context.', 'NULL', 'website', 'objectives', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('258', 'Great Books & Company; Comparative Politics; Globalisation, Flows and Localities; The Anthropology of Health; Institutions and Inequality; Migrations and Integration; Multi-level Democracy in Europe; Cultural Politics; State and mobility; Aids, Medic', 'ine and Human Rights; Families and Health; Labour Market Institutions and Globalisation; Social Inequality in Institutions.', 'NULL', 'website', 'curriculum', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('258', 'Lectures, workgroups, internship, tutoring, independent research fieldwork.', 'NULL', 'NULL', 'website', 'instruction modes', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('258', 'Tuition fees are adjusted annually, for up to date information please see www.uva.nl/isp\n', 'NULL', 'NULL', 'website', 'tuition fee', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('258', 'Graduates of this programme will be able to work in academic or non-academic research environments. The programme provides a good foundation for PhD study, as well as for work in public research organisations and non-academic research institutions in', ' the private sector.\n\nThe Amsterdam Institute for Social Science Research offers PhD programmes in the field of social sciences.', 'NULL', 'website', 'job perspective', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('258', 'This two-year programme starts in September. It consists of\n\n10 ECTS in required courses\n30 ECTS in electives from the thematic specialisation\n50 ECTS in the field of research methodology (including a research-oriented internship)and an independent r', 'esearch project resulting in a manuscript or academic article, to be submitted for publication in a peer-reviewed academic journal (30 ECTS, thus totalling 120 ECTS credits).\n\nFor more information on the curriculum, please visit our website.', 'NULL', 'website', 'curriculum', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('261', 'Na afronding van de master is er een scala aan mogelijkheden op de arbeidsmarkt. Een afgestudeerd socioloog bezit gedegen onderzoeksvaardigheden, sociologische kennis en de capaciteit om zelfstandig complexe maatschappelijke problemen op een vernieuw', 'ende wijze in kaart te brengen en te verwoorden. Bijvoorbeeld in (beleids-)adviezen en artikelen. \nDe master sociologie leidt studenten echter niet op tot een duidelijk afgebakend beroep. ', 'NULL', 'website', 'job perspective', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('261', 'De master heeft een omvang van 60 ECTS (n studiejaar). De specialisatie Algemene Sociologie is opgebouwd uit:\n\nCapita Selecta Social Theory (10 ECTS)\nMethods (2 x 5 ECTS)\nSpecialisatiemodule (10 ECTS)\nSpecialisatiemodule / Keuzemodule (10 ECTS)\nM', 'asterscriptie (20 ECTS)\n\nVoor meer informatie over het curriculum, zie onze website.', 'NULL', 'website', 'curriculum', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('262', 'Tuition fees are adjusted annually, for up to date information please see www.uva.nl/isp', 'NULL', 'NULL', 'website', 'tuition fee', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('262', 'Theres a great need for good programmers in both the commercial sector and the field of research. The programme will help you become a better programmer and understand every aspect of the software engineering process. You learn how to reflect and ', 'analyse situations, which allows you to objectively assess both your own work and that of others. Graduates are therefore highly sought after on the labour market and tend to move up the career ladder quite quickly.', 'NULL', 'website', 'job perspective', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('264', 'De master kent een verplicht vak: beginselen van de democratische rechtsstaat De overige 50 EC worden gevuld met gebonden en vrije keuzevakken en practica, zoals: Vrijheid van Meningsuiting en Politieke Grondrechten, Bestuur en Privaatrecht, European', ' Constitutional Law, Comparative Constitutional Law, Vreemdelingenrecht en Wetgevingspracticum', 'NULL', 'website', 'curriculum', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('264', 'In vele sectoren, bij de overheid en in de private sector, is vraag naar juristen staats- en bestuursrecht. Als advocaat word je vrijwel dagelijks geconfronteerd met enige vormen van bestuursrecht en een gedegen kennis van dit rechtsgebied brengt uit', 'stekende perspectieven. \nOok als voorbereiding op een politieke carrire vormt deze master een goede eerste stap.', 'NULL', 'website', 'job perspective', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('265', 'Stochastics is the mathematical science that studies randomness. Within stochastics we discern probability theory and mathematical statistics as well as more specific fields such as stochastic operations research and financial mathematics.', 'NULL', 'NULL', 'website', 'objectives', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('265', 'The MSc is rooted in research groups at the Universiteit van Amsterdam, the Vrije Universiteit Amsterdam and the Universiteit Utrecht. These groups harbour a wide variety of specialists in the relevant areas of probability theory; Stochastic Processe', 's; Mathematical Statistics; Industrial Statistics; Stochastic Operations Research; Dynamical Systems and Biostatistics.', 'NULL', 'website', 'curriculum', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('265', 'Lectures, research, seminars, papers.', 'NULL', 'NULL', 'website', 'instruction modes', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('265', 'The aim of the programme is to produce experts that can play a role on the highest level, both from the practical as from the theoretical point of view. Throughout the programme the emphasis is on the development of the necessary mathematical theory,', ' which forms the universal background for the variety of applications. Students will be well prepared for research leading to a PhD. Their strong quantitative abilities will also be in demand in industry or public service.', 'NULL', 'website', 'job perspective', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('266', '10 ec verplicht Beginselen van de democratische rechtsstaat\n20 ec gebondenkeuze ruimte\n20 ec vrije keuzeruimte\n10 ec scriptie', 'NULL', 'NULL', 'website', 'curriculum', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('266', 'Er is vraag naar strafrechtjuristen in de advocatuur en bij de (semi)overheid. Bij de overheid is er plaats voor strafrechtjuristen bij de rechterlijke macht, (rechters en openbaar ministerie) politie en bijzondere opsporingsdiensten, de Ministeries ', 'van Justitie, Binnenlandse Zaken en in mindere mate ook andere departementen. Ook grote gemeenten en semi-overheidsinstanties hebben in toenemende mate behoefte aan academisch gevormde juristen met inzicht in handhavingsproblematiek.', 'NULL', 'website', 'job perspective', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('269', 'Als alumnus Tekst en communicatie beschik je niet alleen over gedegen theoretische kennis van alle aspecten van schriftelijke communicatie, maar heb je ook waardevolle werkervaring opgedaan. Hierdoor biedt dit masterprogramma uitstekende perspectieve', 'n op de arbeidsmarkt. Je kunt bijvoorbeeld terechtkomen in de voorlichting en public relations, bij (ver)taalbureaus, tekst- en adviesbureaus, afdelingen in- en externe communicatie en in de media.', 'NULL', 'website', 'job perspective', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('271', 'This programme is intended for students with a Bachelors degree or the equivalent there of in Theatre Studies. \n\nThe level of the Bachelors degree must be comparable to that of a Dutch Bachelors degree. Students who have completed a differen', 't Bachelors programme in the humanities can also seek admission,\nbut they must be able to show that their Bachelors programme included a substantial number of courses in the field of theatre studies. Admission is on a case-by-case basis.\n', 'NULL', 'website', 'admission', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('271', 'This programme is intended for students with a Bachelors degree or the equivalent there of in Theatre Studies. \n\nThe level of the Bachelors degree must be comparable to that of a Dutch Bachelors degree. Students who have completed a differen', 't Bachelors programme in the humanities can also seek admission,\nbut they must be able to show that their Bachelors programme included a substantial number of courses in the field of theatre studies. Admission is on a case-by-case basis.\n', 'NULL', 'website', 'admission', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('271', 'Theatre Studies in Amsterdam offers its students a broad range of possibilities to get insight into processes of theatrical creation and perception as well as aspects of theatricality in social life on international and national scale.', 'NULL', 'NULL', 'website', 'objectives', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('271', 'The Master"s programme in Theatre Studies yields 60 ECTS credits: 42 credits of courses and a Thesis of 18 credits.', 'NULL', 'NULL', 'website', 'curriculum', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('271', 'Courses are offered as seminars in groups of 10 to 15 students.', 'NULL', 'NULL', 'website', 'instruction modes', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('271', 'Tuition fees are adjusted annually. For up-to-date information, please see www.uva.nl/isp', 'NULL', 'NULL', 'website', 'tuition fee', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('271', 'Graduates in Theatre Studies are qualified to pursue a career in diverse\nareas, including theatre or theatre criticism, government institutions,\ncultural organisations and international festival organisations. Research has\nshown that most graduates f', 'ind a job in their field of study within less than\na year. Many students already become closely associated with the theatre world during their studies, thus acquiring experience and connections that may help them later in finding a job.\n', 'NULL', 'website', 'job perspective', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('275', 'The MA programme in Philosophy prepares students for a teaching career, journalism and other writing professions, as well as for a variety of advisory and managerial jobs in public organisations and government institutions.', 'NULL', 'NULL', 'website', 'objectives', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('275', 'Students can design their own programme based on their own interests, choosing three courses in philosophy from the wide selection of courses offered by the Department of Philosophy. For information you can visit our website.', 'NULL', 'NULL', 'website', 'curriculum', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('275', 'Seminars and tutorials with supervision by specialists devoted to the in-depth study of a variety of topics. Supervised individual research resulting in a thesis. All classes are taught in small groups, with a maximum of 20 students.', 'NULL', 'NULL', 'website', 'instruction modes', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('275', 'Tuition fees are adjusted annually, for up to date information please see www.uva.nl/isp', 'NULL', 'NULL', 'website', 'tuition fee', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('275', 'Wanneer je de opleiding Filosofie hebt gevolgd, beschik je over brede culturele bagage, historisch besef en een sterk ontwikkeld abstractievermogen. Je kunt complexe teksten interpreteren en bent in staat je bevindingen helder te verwoorden. Dat maak', 't je tot een academicus die breed inzetbaar is op de arbeidsmarkt. De meest voorkomende terreinen waarop afgestudeerden terechtkomen, zijn:\n\n-de wetenschap \n-het onderwijs \n-beleid en management \n-publiciteit en voorlichting \n-de journalistiek', 'NULL', 'website', 'job perspective', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('276', 'Tuition fees are adjusted annually, for up to date information please see www.uva.nl/isp', 'NULL', 'NULL', 'website', 'tuition fee', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('276', 'Students who have completed a Research Master"s programme in Philosophy will be familiar with one or more of the sub-areas of philosophy and will have the skills to formulate, analyse and discuss philosophical problems. They will also be able to form', 'ulate and present targeted research questions within a broader research plan. The Research Master"s programme in Philosophy prepares students for postgraduate studies and/or independent research.', 'NULL', 'website', 'job perspective', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('277', 'Na afronding van de master Wijsbegeerte van een bepaald wetenschapsgebied ben je breed opgeleid en beschik je over zeer goede analytische vaardigheden.\n\nDit komt niet alleen van pas als je wetenschappelijke ambities hebt, maar biedt je op allerlei be', 'roepsterreinen, afhankelijk van je studiekeuze, betere perspectieven.', 'NULL', 'website', 'job perspective', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('478', 'De studie Tandheelkunde leidt op tot tandarts. Veel van de afgestudeerden zullen zich dan ook als zelfstandige vestigen in een solo- of groepspraktijk. Daarnaast bestaat bij ACTA de mogelijkheid om te werken in het onderwijs of onderzoek.\n\nJe kunt er', ' ook voor kiezen om na afronding van de master verder te specialiseren in een van de deelgebieden van de tandheelkunde. Hiertoe biedt ACTA verschillende postinitile opleidingen aan. Zie voor meer informatie hierover de ACTA-website.', 'NULL', 'website', 'job perspective', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('479', 'Het intensieve masterprogramma is een goed gestructureerde, multidisciplinaire opleiding en leidt je op om zelfstandig onderzoek te doen in Latijns Amerika.\n\nJe wordt vertrouwd gemaakt met de belangrijkste ontwikkelingen van de regio, verschillende t', 'heorien en wetenschappelijke debatten over de oorzaken en betekenis van die ontwikkelingen en met het methodologische instrumentarium dat nodig is om succesvol onderzoek te doen in Latijns Amerika.', 'NULL', 'website', 'job perspective', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('479', 'The CMP research project consists of 40 ECs in total:\n5 ECs field work reports of the research done in Latin America\n5 ECs post fieldwork course\n25 ECs Master thesis\nEach student conducts 3 months of field research in Latin America \n', 'NULL', 'NULL', 'website', 'study abroad', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('479', 'Tuition for the CMP is  2650 for the entire study. Students who successfully complete the first 40 of the total 75 credits (ECs) within the required time limit are eligible for a research grant of maximum  1000 to meet costs during their resear', 'ch training in Latin America.', 'NULL', 'website', 'tuition fee', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('479', 'The CEDLA Masters Programme is aimed toward the study and research of current developments in Latin America, as well as their historical background. From the perspective of different disciplines, attention is given to the most important issues in ', 'the region, including the characteristics of the Latin American continent and the manner in which recent processes of globalisation are changing the living conditions of the inhabitants. \n', 'NULL', 'website', 'objectives', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('479', 'Required Introduction course Democracy, Identity and Sustainable Development \nAims:\n-building an analytical and cognitive foundation as preparation for the more specialised courses that follow\n-creating common terms of reference for those stude', 'nts from different backgrounds who have begun the CMP. \n-testing the knowledge and skills of students so that potential deficiencies can be caught at an early stage. \nForm: lectures and student participation in class\n', 'NULL', 'website', 'curriculum', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('479', 'Additional courses:\n25 ECs in addition to the preparatory fieldwork course (5ECs):MA courses that provide an in-depth study of one of the CMP research themes\nThesis - Fieldwork - Post-fieldwork\nThe CMP students are supervised by the CEDLA research st', 'aff during their fieldwork research and when writing their graduate thesis. Although students choose their own research themes it is advisable to either participate in the ongoing research of research staff.\n', 'NULL', 'website', 'international', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('479', 'Study load: 75 ECs lasting 15 months. The first part of the programme earns 40 ECs and is made up of course work. You take courses, complete various assignments, and write papers. The introductory course and preparatory fieldwork course are mandatory', '; in addition you have a choice of various other masters courses. The second part is given to your research project, which earns 35 ECs. This period will be spent doing fieldwork in Latin America and writing a masters thesis.', 'NULL', 'website', '1st year', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('482', 'Our goal is to give students a high-quality business and management education to enable them to develop into effective leaders. Leaders who convey what our MBA stands for: internationally oriented and with a strong understanding of the importance of ', 'a genuine personal approach.', 'NULL', 'website', 'objectives', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('482', 'Amsterdam Leadership Programme, HRM, Operations & Process Management,Quantative Methods, International Study Trip, Marketing Strategy, Financial Accounting, Corporate Strategy, Thesis.\nFor more information about the courses 2011-2012, please see www.', 'studeren.uva.nl/english_mba.', 'NULL', 'website', 'curriculum', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('482', 'Lectures, case studies, group work, presentations.', 'NULL', 'NULL', 'website', 'instruction modes', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('482', 'The deadline to be eligible for the early-bird tuition fee of  26,000 is March 1, 2012.\nThe deadline to receive a 5% discount if you pay your tuition fee at once is April 30, 2012.\nThe deadline to be eligible for the MBA Tuition Waiver Scheme is M', 'ay 31, 2012.\nTuition fees are adjusted annually. For up-to-date information, please see www.uva.nl/isp', 'NULL', 'website', 'tuition fee', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('482', 'GRE or GMAT test:\n1) GRE -  620 (quantitative)and around 4.0 for analytical writing (the combined score should be 1200 or higher),\n2) GMAT - around 600 and a minimum analytical writing score of around 4.0', 'NULL', 'NULL', 'website', 'admission', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('482', 'Typically, graduates go on to careers in areas in which thorough understanding of the complexities of international business is essential, such as multinational organisations, international consultancy firms, international financial institutions and ', 'banks. Our personal career service helps students make sound career choices and assists them in areas such as writing a cover letter, preparing a professional CV and good interviewing techniques.', 'NULL', 'website', 'job perspective', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('482', 'For more information about admission, please see \nwww.abs.uva.nl/mba\nwww.studeren.uva.nl/mba.', 'NULL', 'NULL', 'website', 'admission', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
