('490', 'The Master"s programme in Artistic Research takes an experimental approach to both specific art objects and broader artistic concepts and opens them up to interpretation. Topics and strategies relevant for current scholarly debates and contemporary a', 'rtistic practice are central.', 'NULL', 'website', 'objectives', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('490', 'The Master"s programme in Artistic Research yields 120 ECTS credits: 30 credits for core courses of the Research MA Art Studies, 40 credits for core courses combining theory and practice and 20 credits for electives.', 'NULL', 'NULL', 'website', 'curriculum', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('490', 'Seminars and tutorials with supervision by specialists devoted to the in-depth study of a variety of topics. Supervised individual research resulting in a thesis. All classes are taught in small groups, with a maximum of 20 students.', 'NULL', 'NULL', 'website', 'instruction modes', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('490', 'Tuition fees are adjusted annually. For up-to-date information, please see www.uva.nl/isp.', 'NULL', 'NULL', 'website', 'tuition fee', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('490', 'Artists with a Master"s degree in Artistic Research will have a distinct advantage when applying to PhD programmes in the fields of art research and art practice. Their ability to formulate theoretical concepts in relation to their artistic practice ', 'enhances their ability to develop their own work and find exhibition and performance venues in which to present it.', 'NULL', 'website', 'job perspective', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('749', 'Door het hoge niveau van het programma, gekoppeld aan een grondige opleiding in analytische vaardigheden, heb je als afgestudeerde in het Informatierecht uitstekende vooruitzichten op de arbeidsmarkt.', 'NULL', 'NULL', 'website', 'job perspective', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('754', 'De master Publieksgeschiedenis leidt je op tot publiekshistoricus. Publiekshistorici gaan uit van hun vaardigheden en kennis als historicus, maar gebruiken deze zodanig dat het beoogde publiek bereikt wordt.', 'NULL', 'NULL', 'website', 'job perspective', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('12004', 'NULL', 'NULL', 'NULL', 'brochure', 'brochure', 'http://www.vu.nl/nl/opleidingen/bacheloropleidingen/brochures/index.asp'),
('12004', 'Het AUC heeft een breed internationaal netwerk. De internationale partneruniversiteiten zijn zorgvuldig geselecteerd op kwaliteit van onderwijs, voorzieningen, en geografische spreiding. ', 'NULL', 'NULL', 'website', 'study abroad', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('12004', 'Big questions and real-world issues\nThe AUC programme combines breadth of experience with depth of knowledge. A key aspect is tackling the real-life problems and challenges facing today"s world. From day one, you are expected to think about the "Big ', 'Questions" in science and society, and learn how to make a meaningful contribution to current debates. As today"s students, but also tomorrow"s leaders, you will have to be successful in both cooperating and competing at an international level.', 'NULL', 'website', 'objectives', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('12004', 'Opportunities to follow courses on a wide variety of subjects\nSmall international classes \nSubstantial freedom in designing your own study programme\nSupport and advice from a personal tutor \nA focus on far-reaching themes and real-world problems in s', 'cience and society\nLearning about the relationships between fields of knowledge, as well as building specialist knowledge \nAdvancing your personal and social development in addition to your intellectual skills', 'NULL', 'website', 'instruction modes', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('12004', 'The AUC liberal arts and sciences programme is rather different from traditional, single subject, university programmes. In addition to providing depth of knowledge, the AUC programme places particular emphasis on:\n\nIntegrating insights\nScientific re', 'asoning\nIntercultural competences\nCommunity engagement\nAcademic projects\n', 'NULL', 'website', 'curriculum', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('12004', 'Whether or not you will actually be offered a place at AUC will depend on your:\n-academic excellence: you must demonstrate your ability to meet the academic demands of the AUC programme \n-level of proficiency in English and mathematics \n-motivation a', 'nd ambition to study an intensive and broad programme \n-commitment to contribute to AUC"s international student and campus life\nFor more information see: www.auc.nl/admissions', 'NULL', 'website', 'admission', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
