('757', 'The Master"s programme in Religious Studies yields 60 ECTS credits: 40 credits for core courses, electives and tutorials and 20 credits for a Master"s thesis. The general track allows for a combination of courses from the six other tracks together wi', 'th other courses in the humanities.', 'NULL', 'website', 'curriculum', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
