('758', 'The Erasmus Mundus Master"s programme in International Performance Research yields 90 ECTS credits: 60 credits for core courses and electives and 30 credits for a research project/Master"s thesis.', 'NULL', 'NULL', 'website', 'curriculum', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('758', 'Seminars and tutorials with supervision by specialists devoted to the in-depth study of a variety of topics. Supervised individual research resulting in a thesis.', 'NULL', 'NULL', 'website', 'instruction modes', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('758', 'Tuition fees are adjusted annually. For up-to-date information, please see www.uva.nl/isp\n\n', 'NULL', 'NULL', 'website', 'tuition fee', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('758', 'This programme equips students with the intellectual and creative skills necessary to be able to conduct research in theatre and performance in an international context and achieve a high degree of competence in this emerging field. This will enable ', 'them to function as well-trained scholar-artists in an international arena in professions ranging from academic to practice-oriented performing arts careers.', 'NULL', 'website', 'job perspective', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('759', 'The two-year Research Master"s programme in Public International Law aims to give students knowledge and understanding of fundamental principles of public international law and, in particular, key areas of the international rule of law, legal science', ' and international legal research.', 'NULL', 'website', 'objectives', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('759', 'Theories and Methods of Legal Research; Legal English; Academic Writing; the International Rule of Law; Law of Public International Organizations, International Human Rights Law; International and European Law in the National Legal Order; State Respo', 'nsability; International Criminal Law; Research Training.', 'NULL', 'website', 'curriculum', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
