('779', 'Accordingly, there are virtually no unemployed OR graduates and job perspectives can be regarded as excellent. Graduates are qualified to work in areas such as:\n\n-Industry (manufacturing)\n-Distribution\n-Servicing (call centers, recreational parks)\n-L', 'ogistical companies and supermarket chains\n-Financial Services (banks, insurance companies)\n-Public transportation (railways, airports)\n-Technical engineering companies (construction)\n-Health services-Logistical and simulation consultancy', 'NULL', 'website', 'job perspective', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
