('797', 'The curriculum of the Youth and Media track of the Master in Communication Science in the first semester consists of two required core courses Youth as media consumers" (12 EC) and\nClashing views on youth and the media" (12 EC), a method course', ' (6 EC). In the second semester, students complete two elective modules of 6 EC each and write a Master"s thesis (18 EC). Students must obtain a total of 60 credits to be awarded the degree.\n\n', 'NULL', 'website', 'curriculum', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
