('807', 'The Institute welcomes individuals with a focused interest in addiction research and treatment, Master"s and PhD students, NGO staff working on addiction-related issues, professionals in human services, practitioners and advocates.\n', 'NULL', 'NULL', 'website', 'admission', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
