('807', 'The programme consists of four courses that each run for one week. The scientific directors will moderate each course. The last week, the main focus will be the integration of new research findings in addiction treatment and possible directions for t', 'he further development of new interventions. Lectures will address the application of insights about implicit drugs-related cognitions, the use of new medications and the introduction of e-health and online interventions in addiction treatment. ', 'NULL', 'website', 'curriculum', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
