('812', 'To provide participants with knowledge and training regarding theories and methods of sexuality research. Participants will develop insight into methods and techniques of the cross-cultural study of sexuality and gender, and are able to use this know', 'ledge in designing, developing and working in research projects.', 'NULL', 'website', 'objectives', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
('812', 'Morning classes are for all students. In the afternoon the programme consists of two tracks: track 1 is designed for those who can indicate a sincere commitment to the study of sexuality. Track 2 is specifically for students with an elaborated resear', 'ch proposal related to the field, and includes a research seminar.', 'NULL', 'website', 'curriculum', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
