('833_parttime', 'This Masters programme offers a specialisation in European Private Law, based on a coherent set of courses on the topics at the heart of the harmonisation of private law in Europe. The elective courses (20 ECTS) offered are: European Consumer Law,', ' European Property Law, European Tort Law, Anthropology of European Private Law, Contract Law and Competition Law, European Company Law II, European Family Law I, Private Law Theory, Anglo-American Contract and Tort Law and European Insolvency Law. \n', 'NULL', 'website', 'curriculum', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
