('150_parttime', 'In forencic research, there is a growing need for scientists who can combine know-how in the fields of chemistry, biology, computer science or statistics with knowledge in the fields of criminology and law. The Forensic Science study programme trains', ' students to be innovative researchers or policy-makers who can make a contribution to the development of forensic science.', 'NULL', 'website', 'objectives', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
