('1000', 'The Real Estate Finance track of the MSc in Business Economics is ideal for those students seeking a career in the real estate and related finance industries.\nThis specialisation gives graduates a definite advantage in their future careers, since the', 'y will know how to analyse both quantitative and qualitative characteristics of commercial property assets as managed within a dynamic business environment.', 'NULL', 'website', 'job perspective', 'http://studieadres.nl'),
